1. *Prekinuo* je igru zbog kiše. (He stopped playing because of the rain.)
2. Nisam mogao da *prekinem* da razmišljam o tome. (I couldn't stop thinking about it.)
3. On je *prekinut* dok je govorio. (He was interrupted while he was speaking.)
4. Juče je *prekinula* s njim. (She broke up with him yesterday.)
5. *Prekinuli* su vezu nakon dugogodišnjeg prijateljstva. (They ended their relationship after a long-time friendship.)

Translation:

1. He stopped playing because of the rain.
2. I couldn't stop thinking about it.
3. He was interrupted while he was speaking.
4. She broke up with him yesterday.
5. They ended their relationship after a long-time friendship.